metadata.name: Description_surface
metadata.description:
Description – the name of the work, at the same time its essence and its constituent
element, does the word contain the essence of things, or is it a contract of the parties?
Two–dimensional space is our three–dimensional vision presented on
a plane - a 3-dimensional model scan embodied in two-dimensional printing
on silk. Three-dimensional space is a 3D model printed on a 3D
printer. The work is a demonstration and research, but can be
created under an individual request.
The NFT itself is a collection, the sum of all media and media, each of them
it is a fixation of reality, but each has its own limitations and
does not fully describe it.The deconstruction of form has led to the study
of ways of describing and deconstructing meanings.
The process of exploring the form through different mediums shows that
each of the variants is a self-sufficient work of art, but at the
same time does not fully describe reality.
